{"tid":2329574,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"納斯達克指數再創歷史新高","createTime":"2020-12-17T10:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T03:46:35.000Z","uid":79081,"like":113,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"75a94128e10b4b8da357bc72488c8097ccdae908","tid":2329574,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:06:04.000Z","msg":"而家係2020年12月17號<br />\n納斯達克指數現報12658.19點<br />\n<br />\n仲有約4個半小時就開市<br />\n<br />\n再次不記名統計,大家對美股的預期觀望<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:Stock only goes up , 黎緊將會係14000點或以上  , 而家只係升浪開端 , 將會不問價掃貨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:泡沫大到不能想象 , 前所未見 , 即將滅世爆破 , 已經/將會一股不留 , 清倉等睇戲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除此之外,有任何睇法大家都可以留低<br />\n另外大家都可以講下係2020年持倉表現<br />\n只作數據參考用<br />\n利伸:只玩正股,半年profit~35%"},{"pid":"dea268a107595b29e477ea3cf0c0275979bb5ca3","tid":2329574,"uid":103647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:07:19.000Z","msg":"無限印銀紙呀,點會唔升呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b895f4c9fea5f3e9547ed465735edf69aa479a62","tid":2329574,"uid":79081,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dea268a107595b29e477ea3cf0c0275979bb5ca3","tid":2329574,"uid":103647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:07:19.000Z","msg":"無限印銀紙呀,點會唔升呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:08:45.000Z","msg":"當然有好大影響,但未必係主因...<br />\n不宜過份吹捧"},{"pid":"9dc6f10b069637f77c8af3d6cba898d195feded8","tid":2329574,"uid":144736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b895f4c9fea5f3e9547ed465735edf69aa479a62","tid":2329574,"uid":79081,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dea268a107595b29e477ea3cf0c0275979bb5ca3","tid":2329574,"uid":103647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:07:19.000Z","msg":"無限印銀紙呀,點會唔升呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/